(46313, 1, 9544, '<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">1.  Users Rules of Conduct</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin"><span class="red_span">HAMMU LTD</span> operates the HAMMU Website, the HAMMU Mobile App and related Apps (collectively, "App"). This Terms and Conditions of Use Agreement ("Agreement") informs users concerning the rules and policies that govern use of the App. The term "user" includes any person who downloads the App or accesses the Website. Users are expected to follow all posted guidelines and rules. For the purposes of this Agreement, the term "HAMMU" (or "we" or "us" or "our") includes, individually and collectively, <span class="red_span">HAMMU LTD</span>, our officers, directors, agents, employees, representatives,  shareholders, parents, partners, licensees, affiliates, subsidiaries, related entities, successors and assigns.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Your use of the App constitutes your agreement to be bound by this Agreement. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE WITH ANY OF THE TERMS OF THIS AGREEMENT, OR ANY POSTED GUIDELINES, POLICIES OR RULES, PLEASE DO NOT USE THE APP.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">2.  License to Use the App</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">HAMMU grants you a limited, non-exclusive license to access and use the App for your own personal, non-commercial purposes.  This license is personal to you and it may not be sublicensed or assigned to anyone else.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Except as expressly authorized by HAMMU in writing, you will not reproduce, redistribute, sell, create derivative works from, decompile, reverse engineer, or disassemble the App or any part of the App.  Nor will you take any actions that may interfere with the operation of the App or cause harm to HAMMU.  All rights not expressly granted by HAMMU in this Agreement are reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">3.  Registration</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">To use the App, you must register.  By doing so, you authorize us to access certain information in your Facebook account, including information about your Facebook friends. By granting us access to your Facebook account, you expressly acknowledge and agree that we may obtain and share your name and a profile picture. Please carefully guard your password and contact us at support@hammu.datingif you believe your account has been accessed by an unauthorized person.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">To use or to participate in certain of the activities, features, functions or services on the App you may be requested to provide certain information about yourself, including your name and contact information ("Personal information"). We may also obtain non-personal information regarding your use to protect the security of other users or the App or to make the App''s content more useful for all users.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">All information obtained by the App from users shall be governed by our Privacy Policy which is posted on the App and is incorporated by reference into this Agreement. If there is a conflict between any term in this Agreement concerning information obtained from users and our Privacy Policy, the term in the Privacy Policy shall prevail.  You should carefully review our Privacy Policy to understand our information collection, use and disclosure practices.  You are responsible for providing accurate and complete information to us in connection with your use of the App. If, at any time, we discover that you have provided false information or have violated any term of this Agreement or our Privacy Policy, your use of the App will be canceled without notice.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">HAMMU is not liable or responsible for any claims relating to any inaccurate, untimely, false or incomplete information provided to us, or from a user''s failure to fully comply with any provision of this Agreement. If necessary, and in accordance with applicable law, we will cooperate with local, state and/or federal authorities to protect the App, users of the App, or HAMMU and to prevent the unauthorized use of the App.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">4.  Your Representations and Warranties</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">You represent and warrant that, in addition to the other representations and warranties made by you in this Agreement, you will (a) comply with all applicable laws, rules and other regulations in connection with the App; (b) not interfere with or disrupt networks connected to the App; (c) not use the App to infringe any third party''s copyright, patent, trademark, trade secret or other proprietary rights or rights of publicity or privacy; (d) not state or imply that any statements you make are endorsed or approved by HAMMU without our prior written consent; and (e) not provide false, inaccurate or misleading information to us or to any user of the App.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">You further represent and warrant that you have the right, authority and capacity to enter into this Agreement and to abide by all of the terms and conditions of this Agreement. If you use the App, you represent and warrant that you are not required to register as a sex offender with any government entity.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">5.  App Content</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">HAMMU shall not be liable for any inaccuracies, errors or omissions on the App. Although we do not have any obligation to correct errors, inaccuracies or omissions on the App, we reserve the right to correct such errors, inaccuracies or omissions without prior notice.  In addition, we reserve the right to change, remove, or update information on the App at any time without prior notice and we may change, suspend or remove all or any aspect of the App at any time without prior notice.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">This Agreement may be revised from time to time without notice. Any changes in our Terms and Conditions of Use will be incorporated into a revised Agreement that will be posted on the App.  Unless otherwise specified, such changes shall be effective when posted. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">6.  Restrictions on Use of the App Content</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Content on the App provided by HAMMU, its affiliates, agents and other sources is protected by copyright, trademark, service mark, patent, trade secret, or other proprietary rights and laws. Except as expressly permitted by us in writing, users are prohibited from copying, reproducing, republishing, uploading, posting, transmitting, distributing, selling, licensing, renting, publicly displaying or performing, editing, adapting or creating a derivative work of any content or other elements obtained from the App, including code and software. Requests for such permission shall be sent by e-mail to support@hammu.dating.  The decision to grant or deny permission is within our sole discretion. Notwithstanding the above, users may print or download content from the App solely for their personal non-commercial use.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">If you have a good faith belief that any content on the App infringes your copyrighted work, you may notify us in accordance with the requirements set forth in the Digital Millennium Copyright Act ("DMCA"), 17 U.S.C. Â§ 512, and request that we remove or block access to the infringing content.  The requestshallincludethefollowing:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">â€¢	identification and description of the copyrighted work claimed to have been infringed;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">â€¢	identification and location on the App of the allegedly infringing content;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">â€¢	statement by you that you have a good faith belief that the allegedly infringing content is not authorized by the copyright owner;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">â€¢	a statement by you, under penalty of perjury, that the information in your request is accurate and that you are either the copyright owner or authorized to act on behalf of the copyright owner; and</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">â€¢	your signature or the signature of a person authorized to act on your behalf. If you have a good faith belief faith that a notice of copyright infringement has been wrongfully filed against you because of content posted on the App, the DMCA allows you to send us a counter-notice. Notices and counter-notices must meet the statutory requirements imposed by the DMCA; see www.loc.gov/copyright. Noticesand counter-noticesshouldbesentto:</p>\r\n\r\n<span class="red_span">HAMMU LTD</span><br>\r\n<span class="red_span">STREET</span><br>\r\n<span class="red_span">ZIP CITY</span><br>\r\n<span class="red_span">COUNTRY</span><br>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">7.  Minimum Age to Use the App</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Parts of the App may require that you be a minimum age to participate in and/or use certain functions or benefits of the App.  Where a minimum age is posted, you must meet the designated minimum age requirements for the specific activity or event.  Requirements and rules for participation in specific activities on the App will be posted on the App. In all events, HAMMU will not knowingly collect personal information from users under 18 years of age.  If we learn of the participation of a person under 18 years of age (or where applicable, under an older posted minimum age) in any such activity, his or her registration or participation will be immediately canceled and all personal information will be deleted from our files.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">8.  Registration to Use App Services and Features</h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Registration may be required for certain App services, features or functions and users may be required to provide a user name and password. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password and any account information. You agree to immediately notifyHAMMU of any unauthorized use of your password or other account information and you further agree to indemnify and hold us harmless for any improper or illegal use of your password.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">We encourage you to contact us regarding any changes in your account, personal contact and e-mail information. If your e-mail address is canceled or becomes inactive or inaccessible for an extended period of time, we reserve the right to cancel your account and delete all or part of your personal information to the extent allowed by law and in accordance with our security measures. We also reserve the right to cancel your account for any or all App activities if you violate any provision of this Agreement and/or our Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">The use of certain App services, features or functions may require that you purchase credits which can be applied to access and use such services, features or functions. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">9.  E-mail </h2>\r\n\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Your e-mail address and the content of any e-mail you send to us will be used by HAMMU for correspondence and response purposes. Any personal information transmitted with an e-mail, such as the sender''s name, e-mail address or home address, will be protected in accordance with our Privacy Policy.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">10.  Non-Personal Information</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Any non-personal information provided by you, whether by e-mail or other transmission to the App, including, but not limited to, feedback, data, answers, questions, comments, suggestions, plans, ideas or the like, shall be deemed to be non-confidential and will not be protected from disclosure.  HAMMU shall be free to use, reproduce, disclose and distribute non-confidential and non-personal information to others without liability or restriction. You hereby grant us an irrevocable, transferable, fully paid up, royalty-free, perpetual, non-exclusive worldwide license to use, copy, print, display, modify, publish, reproduce, transmit, edit, distribute and otherwise exploit the non-confidential information sent to us, and to create and exploit derivative works therefrom, in any form, medium, or technology now known or later developed, for any purpose whatsoever, with or without attribution to you. </p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class="ow_smallmargin">11.  Your Responsibilities and Obligations</h2>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">In using the App, you agree to conduct yourself in a civil and respectful manner.  You are responsible for all content and materials that you post or otherwise make available to the App.  You agree not to upload, email, post, publish, distribute, transmit or otherwise make available to the App any content or material that:</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(a) is unlawful, harassing, defamatory, libelous, abusive, threatening, harmful, racist, or otherwise objectionable;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(b) promotes bigotry, hatred or harm to any group or individual;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(c) exploits persons under 18 years of age in a sexual or violent manner;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(d) solicits personal information from anyone under 18 years of age;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(e) provides instruction regarding illegal activities;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(f) interferes with another user''s use and enjoyment of the App.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(g) constitutes unauthorized advertising, unauthorized solicitation for goods or services, or solicitation of funds;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(h) constitutes unsolicited bulk e-mail, junk mail, spam, contests, or chain letters;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(i) is intended to interrupt, destroy or limit the functionality or integrity of any computer software;</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">(j) violates any applicable laws or regulations.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">Any conduct by a user of the App that violates this Agreement in any way may result in the suspension or termination of the user''s registration and use of  the App.  Submissions or postings by you to the App will be posted in public areas on the App. HAMMU shall not be responsible for the action of any users or third parties with respect to any information, materials or content posted, uploaded or transmitted in, on, or through the App.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">By participating in any of the App services or features, you agree to follow the Terms and Conditions of Use as set forth in this Agreement. Postings to public areas may not always be reviewed by HAMMU prior to appearing on the App and we reserve the right to a) change, delete, or remove, in part or in full, any such postings; b) terminate or suspend access to such areas for conduct that we believe, in our sole discretion, interferes with others'' use of the App; and/or c) cooperate if deemed necessary with local, state, and/or federal authorities in accordance with applicable law.</p>\r\n<p class="ow_smallmargin">You must be at least 18 years of age to use or participate in the App''s services and features.  HAMMU will not accept registrations or knowingly allow the use of or participation in its App services or features by persons under 18 years of age. HAMMU may allow users to post comments ("Comments") which are governed by the terms of this Agreement. Such Comments do not necessarily reflect the views of HAMMU or its employees, subsidiaries, agents, licensees and affiliates, and we do not assume responsibility or liability for any Comments or for any claims, damages, or losses resulting from the posting of any Comments. Comments that are submitted to the App shall be owned exclusively and in perpetuity by us, and we and our employees, subsidiaries, agents, licensees and affiliates shall have the unrestricted, perpetual, and exclusive right to use, reproduce, modify, translate, transmit, distribute or otherwise exploit any and all materials and communications. We have no obligation to give credit or pay any consideration to you 